    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, some fading paint on the roof, and a small dent in the rear quarter panel. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold. Mechanically, the car starts and runs fine, though it will likely need new brakes and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics.",
