      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle presents a distinguished profile, characterized by its mechanical integrity and well-preserved aesthetic. Having undergone a rigorous professional inspection, it stands as a testament to diligent maintenance and responsible ownership. We are proud to offer this exceptional automobile, which seamlessly combines sophisticated performance with enduring value for the serious driver.",
      "price": 33850.0,
